stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> UNIDENTIFIED_UNENRICHED : discovery (cell encounter)

    state "UNIDENTIFIED_UNENRICHED" as UNIDENTIFIED_UNENRICHED
    state "UNIDENTIFIED_ENRICHED" as UNIDENTIFIED_ENRICHED
    state "IDENTIFIED" as IDENTIFIED
    state "DONATED" as DONATED
    state "PLACED" as PLACED
    state "RELEASED" as RELEASED
    state "TRADED" as TRADED

    note right of UNIDENTIFIED_UNENRICHED
        Item discovered, species not yet enriched.
        Silhouette display.
        Hold gesture does nothing.
    end note

    note right of UNIDENTIFIED_ENRICHED
        Species enrichment complete.
        Silhouette but responds to hold gesture.
    end note

    note right of IDENTIFIED
        Full TCG card revealed.
        Stats rolled (brawn / wit / speed).
        Art revealed, affixes assigned.
    end note

    note right of DONATED
        Permanently placed in a sanctuary collection.
        Leaves pack. Irreversible.
    end note

    note right of PLACED
        In sanctuary display (not collection slot).
        Visual only. Removable.
    end note

    note right of RELEASED
        Removed from inventory. Gone.
    end note

    note right of TRADED
        Transferred to another player.
    end note

    UNIDENTIFIED_UNENRICHED --> UNIDENTIFIED_ENRICHED : species enrichment completes\n(server‑side, silent)
    UNIDENTIFIED_ENRICHED --> IDENTIFIED : hold‑to‑reveal\n(client‑side stat roll + animation)
    IDENTIFIED --> DONATED : donate to collection (permanent)
    IDENTIFIED --> PLACED : place in sanctuary (removable)
    IDENTIFIED --> RELEASED : release (destructive)
    IDENTIFIED --> TRADED : trade to player (deferred)
    PLACED --> IDENTIFIED : remove from sanctuary display
